From 021e6212200fba2325f4a99f2323bcf06cd698fd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sergiy Dybskiy <sergiy.dybskiy@sentry.io>
Date: Mon, 11 May 2026 20:58:11 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Add severe weather alert banner and expand default locations

Show a banner near the top of the main screen when alerts are
enabled and the current condition is thunderstorms or heavy rain.
Add Chicago to default locations with windy conditions data.
Wire up error monitoring for both app and API server.
